headline: United Airlines price target lowered to $89 from $103 at Seaport Research
summary: Seaport Research lowered the firm’s price target on United Airlines (UAL) to $89 from $103 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. While there are no changes to the firm’s long-term fundamental view, issues at Newark air traffic control impact its six month outlook, the analyst tells investors.
